 of ASL instruction? (ASL 1, ASL 2, ASL 3, and ASL 4)  for $79.95?  \nSee \"SuperUSB\" in the ASLUniversity bookstore at: https://lifeprint.com/bookstore/bookstore.htm\n\nFor free ASL Lessons see: https://www.youtube.com/billvicars\nTo learn basic fingerspelling see https://youtu.be/va1aAXpVr2w\n\nAbout your instructor:\nhttp://www.lifeprint.com/asl101/pages-layout/instructor.htm\nWarm regards and love to you all.\nI am grateful for your support.\n- Dr. Bill\n:)","isCrawlable":true,"thumbnail":{"thumbnails":[{"url":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/wtURQzK00eo/hqdefault.jpg?sqp=-oaymwEbCKgBEF5IVfKriqkDDggBFQAAiEIYAXABwAEG\u0026rs=AOn4CLAkNSUmA8O9iPfdLTnaqDq9GPC8cQ","width":168,"height":94},{"url":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/wtURQzK00eo/hqdefault.jpg?sqp=-oaymwEbCMQBEG5IVfKriqkDDggBFQAAiEIYAXABwAEG\u0026rs=AOn4CLDEgYK9H15dWQ287YY34tu8EvkJTQ","width":196,"height":110},{"url":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/wtURQzK00eo/hqdefault.jpg?sqp=-oaymwEcCPYBEIoBSFXyq4qpAw4IARUAAIhCGAFwAcABBg==\u0026rs=AOn4CLDD3ADNseSRQtpyk9t-l0hC2KKVfg","width":246,"height":138},{"url":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/wtURQzK00eo/hqdefault.jpg?sqp=-oaymwEcCNACELwBSFXyq4qpAw4IARUAAIhCGAFwAcABBg==\u0026rs=AOn4CLAlVTSIV0Lkdhfr_AhisMrDPJRTUQ","width":336,"height":188},{"url":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi_webp/wtURQzK00eo/maxresdefault.webp","width":1920,"height":1080}]},"allowRatings":true,"viewCount":"33292","author":"Signs","isPrivate":false,"isUnpluggedCorpus":false,"isLiveContent":false,"isTvfilmVideo":false},"playerConfig":{"granularVariableSpeedConfig":{"minimumPlaybackRate":25,"maximumPlaybackRate":200,"stepSize":5,"defaultPlaybackRateOptions":[{"label":"1.0","value":100,"isPremiumUpsell":false,"priority":5},{"label":"1.25","value":125,"isPremiumUpsell":false,"priority":2},{"label":"1.5","value":150,"isPremiumUpsell":false,"priority":3},{"label":"1.75","value":175,"isPremiumUpsell":false,"priority":0},{"label":"2.0","value":200,"isPremiumUpsell":false,"priority":4},{"label":"3.0","value":300,"isPremiumUpsell":true,"priority":1}